iro, and Reine were each facing off with two demon while the 5 from Reines army fought 4. First Iyiro used his whip like weapon, and the demon caught the whip with his hand. The whip was made of metal, and could severally wound pretty much anything, but the demon hide was unussally strong, and capable to withstand the full force of Iyiro's attack. The demon and Iyiro began a tog o war with the whip, while the lashknife scarred the other demon. Iyiro and the first demon kept up the tug o war, while the other approached Iyiro from behind.<br>
<br>
Thruldor kicked the demon closest, and sent him flying, yet the blow hardly phased the demon. The demon got up and now Thruldor was again facing two demons.<br>
<br>
Reine threw his knives at the demons eyes. Somehow the demon dodged even with the slow spell working against it. It appears all the demons had thicker skin, unnaturally thick and that the slow spell was not working. <br>
<br>
The 5 who were fighting off 4 demons were forced to defend the mage. The 4 demons went straight for the mage of the group. The 4 tried to defend the mage, but their wepons were uncapable of peircing the thick hide of the demons. The demons threw the 4 guards aside, only bruising them, but got to the mage and killed him, taking away the haste advantage the adventurers had. The three adventurers looked ontop of a hill, and saw another figure. He seemed to appear out of nowhere, from 100 feet to 10 feet away in the blink of an eye. The 10 demons regrouped around the figure.*<br>
<br>
Unknown: This is demon land you shall die.<br>
<br>
Reine: Who are you?!<br>
<br>
Unknwon: I'll take that as your last request, my name is Malakye. *The figure was 5'11, and seemed to weigh about 180 pounds. His hair and eyes were both a blood red color. He was armed with daggers, yet seemed a bit young to be feared by these 10 other demons. (if you dont realize it this is Emporertim's character that I brought into play as GM, since he has been &quot;busy&quot;. I think he's just dodging me.*<br>
